329
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:33,440
I think

330
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,720
he's the best candidate

331
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,960
for CTO.

332
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,030
You just didn't

333
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:47,120
cherish him.

334
00:14:47,550 --> 00:14:48,750
When you asked him to leave,

335
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,510
