346
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:30,960
Go back home for some rest.

347
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:32,200
OK.

348
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,440
Excuse me.

349
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:41,910
Hello.

350
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,600
