380
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,790
I have to go to the lab.

381
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,630
I'll go with you.

382
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,840
OK.

383
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:29,870
Sir,

384
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,720
please divert

385
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,080
to 201 Material Research.

386
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:33,750
