423
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:32,310
Don't worry.

424
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,200
Here we are.

425
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:33,830
Mrs. Qin,

426
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,720
it was

427
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,680
just a little accident.

428
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,480
No big deal.

429
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:39,000
There you are.

