464
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:25,640
Umm...

465
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:27,030
Just too many oranges.

466
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,310
What?

467
00:21:31,960 --> 00:21:32,960
Does it hurt?

468
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,200
Wounded?

469
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,310
Nothing.

470
00:21:45,350 --> 00:21:46,640
On my way back,

471
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,750
I went to the lab with Professor Liang

