496
00:22:39,070 --> 00:22:40,480
After it's verified,

497
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:42,240
professors will interview you
immediately.

498
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:42,680
Of course,

499
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,310
